18:29.375 --> 18:31.000
I don't know, I'm looking
through the catalog.

18:31.083 --> 18:33.333
I'm wondering
why they don't use
Indian women.

18:41.166 --> 18:42.875
They don't work
in India.

18:44.750 --> 18:46.166
Everything's about skin?

18:47.166 --> 18:49.667
Toboni:
Why aren't there
Indian models?

18:58.375 --> 18:59.792
Toboni:
It's an open secret in India

18:59.875 --> 19:02.875
that fair skin is seen
as the beauty ideal.

19:02.959 --> 19:05.709
But for anyone
hoping to become
a Bollywood star,

19:05.792 --> 19:08.166
it can feel more like
a job requirement.

19:08.250 --> 19:11.125
Kartik Rao:
So this is audition messages.

19:11.208 --> 19:15.625
So big production.
Fair skin or normal skin
I think okay, but good-looking.

19:15.709 --> 19:19.083
So, Kartik is showing me
all of the casting calls
over email,

19:19.166 --> 19:24.417
and at the, you know,
first line of all of them,
it's either fair or very fair.

19:26.834 --> 19:28.959
So you're, like, Bollywood's
casting director.

19:36.333 --> 19:39.000
Well, I'll just kind of be
standing next to you.

19:39.083 --> 19:40.750
Maybe your sidekick?

19:41.250 --> 19:42.792
Well, let's get started.

19:44.375 --> 19:47.000
Toboni:
So what types of actors
are you looking for?

19:47.083 --> 19:50.375
Siddiqui:
Two main leads,
like bride and groom.

19:50.458 --> 19:51.583
Action.

19:58.709 --> 20:00.875
So, I know he will not
get selected.

20:00.959 --> 20:05.667
What the clients tell us,
he should be 5'10" about,

20:05.750 --> 20:08.208
fair-looking,
very dashing look.

20:11.333 --> 20:12.375
Hello.

20:12.458 --> 20:14.417
Hey, baby. I'm home!

20:14.500 --> 20:19.500
I mean, I want to propose you,
but I'm not ready
for the marriage.

20:20.792 --> 20:22.333
How do you
think he did?

20:22.792 --> 20:24.125
-Not good.
-Oh.

20:24.208 --> 20:26.291
Baby, I'm home.

20:30.125 --> 20:32.458
So if somebody's
a great actor,

20:32.542 --> 20:35.208
but they have
a dark complexion,
will you hire them?

20:35.291 --> 20:37.667
(Siddiqui speaking)

21:25.959 --> 21:27.750
♪ ♪

21:28.458 --> 21:31.166
Toboni:
Of course, we wanted
to find out what it was
actually like

21:31.250 --> 21:33.375
on a Bollywood set.

21:47.917 --> 21:50.125
Toboni:
The one thing that's, um,
immediately apparent,

21:50.208 --> 21:55.000
is that the two lead actors
are pretty fair-skinned,
and everyone else is not.

21:59.125 --> 22:00.125
