22:00.208 --> 22:02.875
(cheering)

22:09.458 --> 22:10.542
Toboni:
Are you the--

22:10.625 --> 22:12.583
Are you love interests
in this TV show?

22:12.667 --> 22:14.583
Yes. Yes.

22:15.333 --> 22:17.083
- Papa by Chance?
-Yes.

22:19.792 --> 22:22.959
Uh, that he was
made a father...

22:23.041 --> 22:24.750
All:
By chance.

